| Aspect | Pattern |
|--------|---------|
| **CLI parsing** | Direct argv[2] → COMMANDS lookup in registry.js; args array passed to handler |
| **Error handling** | AppError(message, exitCode); caught in cli.js, stderr.write + process.exit |
| **Command structure** | Single export function; takes args array; returns string array for console output |
| **Data models** | Stateless core functions (allProducts, productById, orderTotal, etc.) |
| **File output** | config.outputDir + `<entity>.<extension>`; --format flag triggers export |
| **Config** | Flat object in config.js; features array tracks subsystems |
| **Tests** | None found in repo (no test patterns yet) |

